high_descs: Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the dining table on your right.
Pick up dish sponge from the desk.
Head straight towards the floor lamp by turning around and turning left.
anns.task_desc: Examine a dish sponge by the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Head rotate and turn left to the dining table.
Pick the dish sponge from the dining table.
Turn left to the floor lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a dish sponge by the light of a tall lamp

high_descs: Turn around and go near the dining table.
Take the dish sponge from the table.
Turn around and go near the floor lamp.
Put the dish sponge near the lamp and it will be glow.
anns.task_desc: To glow the floor lamp using the dish sponge.
